    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Poly Plaza ULTIMATE?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Poly Plaza</strong> <strong>ULTIMATE</strong> is an idle tycoon rpg where you explore an open world to purchase properties and generate passive incomes!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover new ways to get RICH</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase properties to generate passive incomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the worlds to collect new items to sell in shops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft new expensive items for more EXP and cash!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Buy a new vehicle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase a new vehicle to navigate the open world and store more objects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208170/extras/c51e3cc0b089b37be9fd1d5edd4f9ea7.poster.avif?t=1771253123\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208170/extras/c51e3cc0b089b37be9fd1d5edd4f9ea7.webm?t=1771253123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208170/extras/c51e3cc0b089b37be9fd1d5edd4f9ea7.mp4?t=1771253123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a living open world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the big city of Poly Plaza to find new items to collect and new properties to invest in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208170/extras/046d152ac0b5a42742e9cea318464fa1.poster.avif?t=1771253123\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/32081